verses.text: \w Praise|strong="H1984"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Lord, \w O|strong="H8034"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* soul, \w in|strong="H3117"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w life|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3117"\w* \w praise|strong="H1984"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Lord: \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3117"\w* sing \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* God \w as|strong="H3117"\w* \w long|strong="H3117"\w* \w as|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w shall|strong="H3117"\w* \w be|strong="H8034"\w*. Put not \w your|strong="H3605"\w* trust \w in|strong="H3117"\w* princes:

\w In|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* children \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w men|strong="H1419"\w*, \w in|strong="H3068"\w* whom \w there|strong="H0369"\w* \w is|strong="H0369"\w* \w no|strong="H0369"\w* salvation.

\w His|strong="H5046"\w* spirit \w shall|strong="H1755"\w* go forth, \w and|strong="H5046"\w* he \w shall|strong="H1755"\w* return into \w his|strong="H5046"\w* earth: \w in|strong="H1755"\w* \w that|strong="H1755"\w* day \w all|strong="H1755"\w* \w their|strong="H5046"\w* thoughts \w shall|strong="H1755"\w* perish.

Blessed \w is|strong="H1697"\w* he who hath \w the|strong="H1697"\w* God \w of|strong="H1697"\w* Jacob \w for|strong="H1697"\w* \w his|strong="H6381"\w* helper, whose hope \w is|strong="H1697"\w* \w in|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H1697"\w* Lord \w his|strong="H6381"\w* God:

\w Who|strong="H0559"\w* made heaven \w and|strong="H0559"\w* earth, \w the|strong="H0559"\w* sea, \w and|strong="H0559"\w* all \w things|strong="H1420"\w* \w that|strong="H0559"\w* are \w in|strong="H0559"\w* \w them|strong="H0559"\w*.

Who keepeth truth \w for|strong="H7442"\w* ever: who executeth judgment \w for|strong="H7442"\w* them that suffer wrong: who giveth food \w to|strong="H6666"\w* \w the|strong="H6666"\w* hungry. \w The|strong="H6666"\w* Lord looseth them that are fettered:

\w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* enlighteneth \w the|strong="H3068"\w* blind. \w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* lifteth up \w them|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* cast \w down|strong="H0639"\w*: \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* loveth \w the|strong="H3068"\w* just.

\w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* keepeth \w the|strong="H3605"\w* strangers, \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* support \w the|strong="H3605"\w* fatherless \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* widow: \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* ways \w of|strong="H3068"\w* sinners \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w destroy|strong="H3605"\w*.

\w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* reign \w for|strong="H3605"\w* ever: thy \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* Sion, unto generation \w and|strong="H3068"\w* generation.
